Opcode mix tool results:
    *[0-9]* : total executed instructions
#ifdef AARCH64
    *[0-9]* : [a-z ]* \([a-z,A-Z,0-9]*\)
    *[0-9]* : [a-z ]* \([a-z,A-Z,0-9]*\)
    *[0-9]* : [a-z ]* \([a-z,A-Z,0-9]*\)
    *[0-9]* : [a-z ]* \([a-z,A-Z,0-9]*\)
#else
    *[0-9]* : [a-z ]*
    *[0-9]* : [a-z ]*
    *[0-9]* : [a-z ]*
    *[0-9]* : [a-z ]*
#endif
.*
